**Overview**

This dashboard offers a detailed overview of playbook alerts from recordedfuture. A line chart displays playbook alerts over time, helping to identify trends and periods of increased alert activity. The total number of playbook alerts is presented as a metric for quick reference. Several pie charts break down alerts by priority, risk score, and host operating system, providing insight into the severity and environment of the alerts. A bar chart highlights alert distribution by user, revealing which users are most frequently associated with alerts. Additional bar charts show alerts by rule ID and malware family, allowing for analysis of detection patterns and the types of threats being flagged.
